Installation Frontend
NPM = npm install

Installation BACKEND
NODEMON = npm install -g nodemon
EXPRESS = npm install express --save

DATABASE
MONGOOSE = npm install mongoose
___________________

Lancement FRONT
- npm run start

Lancement BACK
- node server
- nodemon server (Apres installation et update en live)

_______________________
!! Installation de Nodemon pour eviter de relancer commande node Server a chaque changement.


